{"tid":1727262,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【區選好重要嗎？】人民無時無刻需監察其授權！否則一年一度賣曬你地啊！","createTime":"2019-11-16T11:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T12:03:31.000Z","uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"994f8589e74235416b3d71a67e792ff869222c35","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主權在民</span></span></strong><br />\n你地唔可以因為11.24大勝, 而交曬比泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">精華</span></span></strong> 呢個睇完 幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">開定先: 陶傑預告成真，區選大勝 ，香港人收貨，永續選舉運動，<span style=\"color: gold;\">義士變comdom</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/exdHrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/exdHrS</a><br />\n<br />\n手足Victor可能區選前進行突擊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n犧牲自己, 阻止永續社運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n數區聯合分成數批遊行大隊表達民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你唔想手足做condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n區選前用你雙腿話比全世界聽你地唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警告：而家出老解嘅策略同俄羅斯侵略克里米亞一樣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1727048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1727048</a><br />\n<blockquote> <br />\n見到大家好似對中共赤裸裸咁出動解放軍無動於衷<br />\n同大家重溫吓俄羅斯係點樣侵佔克里米亞<br />\n俄羅斯派左一班冇著俄羅斯軍服、有禮貌、蒙面嘅「小綠人」去克里米亞<br />\n佢地一直都好和平，同啲local好似冇咩兩句<br />\n到俄羅斯一落命令就立即開打<br />\n請大家spread出去，香港正被侵略<br />\n係克里米亞形式侵略<br />\n<br />\nChina is dispatching their version of the Russian 'Little Green Men' to Hong Kong. Hong Kong will become the next Crimea if the world does not act fast. Spread the word.<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新界</span><br />\n1. 屯門  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n2. 沙田  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n3. 大埔  (參考過往遊行) <br />\n4. 上水  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n5. 荃葵青  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">九龍</span><br />\n6. 油尖旺  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n7. 黃大仙<span style=\"color: red;\"> (可以拼合埋觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />達成九之數, 咒死中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n8. 觀塘 (參考過往遊行)<br />\n9. TKO  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港島</span><br />\n10. 港島  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<br />\n人口分佈<br />\n新界:九龍:港島 ~ 4:2:1<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n規劃署今日（六月八日）發表載列2018年至2026年香港人口分布最新推算數字的「人口分布推算2018－2026」報告書。推算新界及九龍的人口，在2016年至2026年期間，會分別增加441600人及140200人，在2026年其人口會分別達到428萬人及238萬人，而同期間香港島的人口，則由125萬逐漸減少至116萬。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未來主人翁(未滿18歲)冇權投票, 但是有權上街表達拆求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人嚟講, 我相信區選好易被消取<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是<span style=\"color: red;\">希望有人幫手聯合申請 十條路線遊行集結200萬人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n利申非搞手, 有冇手足BUY<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n同埋下星期一黎明行動照常舉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n開始吹風叫停平日黎明行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726255</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ThXJj8O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThXJj8O.png&h=ef75bad8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fb6fc579d72901579189371028a6098493afce4","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:23:46.000Z","msg":"請幫手推"},{"pid":"f62ef5142e09f77e45367566960c0706425ea03b","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:24:07.000Z","msg":"區選有是BONUS, 冇亦唔應該怪責手足"},{"pid":"8a30a702882fc8a7596b23f8d9df3cd422c5c8ea","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:24:20.000Z","msg":"老實講區選只會永續社運"},{"pid":"534488153cd7b71fbee88b4fa682f830dc1fe7e8","tid":1727262,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a1e279b39e224874f1a235e96cc38480d73fb31","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">#1平匡先生&bull;50 分鐘前</span><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n陶傑預言講中<br />\n<br />\n區選大勝，獨立調查委員會成立<br />\n港共清算部份黑警<br />\n普選方案重推<br />\n鴿派管治團隊上台<br />\n香港人收貨<br />\nYeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">實際我答你會點</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1年內</span><br />\n如果真係咁<br />\n絕大部份和理非會收貨<br />\n因為5大訢求 表面上已經成立<br />\n之後同前線割𥱊<br />\n前線手足進退兩難 <br />\n<br />\n鴿派管治團隊 先話特赦 非法集結罪名較輕者<br />\n重嘅 (eg火魔法師)交俾獨立調查委員會 法庭處理<br />\n警隊 交幾個名 再搵外國專家檢視<br />\n藍衫就隨機交名<br />\n<br />\n普選方案 又地區咨詢又成<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2年至3年內</span><br />\n獨立調查委員會報告已出<br />\n部份高官 POPO付上刑責<br />\n泛民 香港人接受<br />\n前線手足被割 要付上刑責<br />\n武力抗爭 得不到民意支持 相繼收皮<br />\n<br />\n政權開始清算 教育、社福、醫護、法律行業<br />\n清算方式 引入人口、利益關係<br />\n<br />\n普選變偽普 再用什麼什麼 按年改革為借口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">不出10年</span><br />\n全面引入監控鏡頭<br />\n以低息貸款為樓價方案<br />\n抗爭成本提高<br />\n人口成功清洗<br />\n<br />\n香港玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7dd45266c94d21c6cd3218126dc0294f9f6c59ba","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:27:16.000Z","msg":"1/20"},{"pid":"cf797d5de543d26a750de399d644303ab5a3f977","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:27:26.000Z","msg":"2/20"},{"pid":"14281835045e11806b8b3b570329c4a8eab7cb30","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:29:51.000Z","msg":"3/20"},{"pid":"2f73110bc2f61696533d59fcc773f8fa51a706c4","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"4/20"},{"pid":"f2e3a6ae413b96891a32311708629300e70e18dc","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"5/20"},{"pid":"d8bfa18bfde178f35935a5dd91a5bbcda5762003","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dc3f7f2a94fb4fd85ee5612850122e28b7827b4","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8d490b815e99f9f8d6cddd62d10f5dbd2ed1eb7","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48a11d83f915391b2ee7561f4170e29256e01346","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cd4b04769675d512856367135ca98ff940990d","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fb4f225a3407b5fc8ac5968d0037d1d84e62e4","tid":1727262,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec84725233c544db046827ca275f4e89eae3dff","tid":